          <widget class="QLineEdit" name="kcfg_DefaultInitialDestination">
           <property name="toolTip">
            <string>Place a genuinely new normal window on desktop:2, desktop-name:Work, output:DP-1, or a desktop selector plus output. Desktop and output names are exact and case-sensitive. An exact application destination rule takes precedence. Blank disables the default.</string>
